quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  10,71,"An Nulaa…óo, qissano …ìee sirkoo…ìe fennoo…ìe, kabaaru Annabu Nuuhu, tuma nde o maakannoo yim…ìe makko …ìen : "Ko onon yo yim…ìe, si tawii √±ii…ìugol am ngol hakkunde mon mawnii e mon, ko waajorta on Aayeeje Alla …óen kadi sattii e mon, on fi…ìii warugol lam, ko e Alla tun woni tuugii mi e bonnugol pewje mon. Fellitee e fiyaaku mon, fi…ìon warugol lam, noddon rewetee…ói mon …óin ko wallitoo on e …óum, refti fewjoore ma…ì…ìe nden wonantaa sirru suu…óii…óo. ∆Åaawo nden e…ì…ìoore mon warugol lam, fewjanee lam ko e…ì…ìu…óon kon, wata on nennitan-am nennitanam ko …ìuri e fan…óude."
  10,72,"Si tawii on …óuurnike e noddaandu am ndun, gom…óii hi…óon anndi mi …óa…ì…ìiraa on njo…ìdi ko mi yottiniri nulal am ngal kon. Njo…ìdi am ndin wonaali si wanaa ka Alla, foti on gom…óin Mo maa hara on yeddu Mo. Alla yamirii lam nde mi laatodto e jebbiloranii …ìe Mo dewal e golle mo∆¥∆¥e …ìen."
  10,73,"Yim…ìe makko …ìen fenni mo, …ìe goonginaali mo. Men da…óndi mo kanko e gom…óim…ìe wonndunoo…ìe e makko ka laana. Men wa…ótini…ìe lonto adinoo…ìe …ìe, Men halkiri …ìen fennu …ìe Aayeeje e hujjaaji …ói o addi …óin haacaango. Tesko an Nulaa…óo, ko honno battane yim…ìe …ìe Nuuhu jertinoo…ìe wa…ói, …ìe gom…óinaano."
  10,74,"Refti …ìaawo dumunna, Men immini …ìaawo Nuuhu Nulaa…ìe faade e yim…ìe mun. Nulaa…ìe mofte ma…ì- …ìe …óen addani …ìe Aayeeje e …ìanngannduyeeji. Kono …ìe alaano muuyaande gom…óingol sabu ko …ìe ha…ì…ìitino kon e fennugol Nulaa…ìe …ìen. Alla noti e …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen. Ko sugu ndee notannde nde Men noti e jokkunoo…ìe Nulaa…ìe yawtunoo…ìe …ìen, Men notirta e …ìer…óe heefer…ìe yawtu…ìe keeri Alla …ìen e kala nokku e jamaanu."
  10,75,"Refti …ìaawo dumunna, Men immini …ìaawo …ìee …óoo Nulaa…ìe, Muusaa e neene-gooto makko on Haaruuna haa e Fir'awna laam…óo Misra on e hooree…ìe dental yim…ìe makko …ìen. Men immindini …ìe e Aayeeje tinndinooje e goongugol ma…ì…ìe. ∆Åe mawnintinanii gom…óingol ko o addi kon, …ìe woni yim…ìe bom…ìe, sabu ko …ìe yeddiri kon Alla …ìe fenni Nulaa…ìe Makko …ìen."
  10,76,"Nde diina kan ka Muusaa e Haaruuna (yo …ìe his) arunoo e Fir'awna e hooree…ìe mbatu makko ngun, …ìe wi'ani …óen Aayeeje tindinooje e goongugol ko Muusaa addi kon : "∆äum ko mbilewu feenyungu, wonaa goonga"."
  10,77,"Muusaa maakinrani …ìe feloore : "E on wi'anay goonga kan tuma ka ari e mon : …óum ko mbilewu? Wanaa non, …óum wanah mbilewu, min mi…óo anndi wonnde mbileejo maletaake abadaa. Ko honno mi jokkirta …óum?""
  10,78,"Yim…ìe Fir'awna …ìen jaabii Muusaa (yo o his), …ìe wi'i : "E a addiran men nguu mbilewu fii yo a suru men gaay e ko men tawri kon baabiraa…ìe amen …ìen e diina, laamu ngun wonana maa an e neene-gooto maa on? Menen men wonaali qirrantoo…ìe on …ói…óo -an Muusaa e Haaruuna- wonnde ko on Nulaa…ìe imminaa…ìe e amen"."